Project for capstone: 

Title : Movie imdb rating

Dataset source 	  : https://www.kaggle.com/tmdb/tmdb-movie-metadata

Problem statement : Predicting which type of movie gets higher rating.

Potential Client  : my analysis will provide help to movie maker on what all factor make affects movie rating.
				    Whether it is mocie subject , director , actors or any other variable which account for movie being highly rated.

Approach          : Initially step which I will follow are :
					1) getting data
					2) analysis of the data i.e all the different varibles and number of observation present in dataset
					3) catagorizing of dataset on different variable. And Identifying feature/variable which we do nnot
					   impact our rating i.e discarding features.
					4) desinging of algorithm which will lead to solution.

